="1 6 1 22 8 18 16 22 23 18 23 2 16 6 8 2 1 6"></polygon><line x1="8" y1="2" x2="8" y2="18"></line><line x1="16" y1="6" x2="16" y2="22"></line></svg> <span class="full_label">More like this</span><span class="mobile_label">Related</span></a></li></ul><script type="text/javascript">new I.GameUserTools('#user_tools')</script><div id="wrapper" class="main wrapper game_page_wrapper"><div id="inner_column" class="inner_column size_medium family_pixel"><div id="header" class="header align_center has_image"><img src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzI1ODMzODA0LnBuZw==/original/RX5FHk.png" title="TINY Farm TRPG ASSETS PACK" alt="Colorful pixel art farm scene with crops, animals, a river, characters, and a house. Large text reads &#039;TINY Farm TRPG ASSETS PACK&#039;."/><h1 itemprop="name" class="game_title">Tiny Farm RPG - Asset Pack [16x16]</h1></div><div id="view_game_1848187" class="view_game_page page_widget base_widget buy_on_top"><div class="header_buy_row"><p>A downloadable asset pack</p><div class="buy_row"><div class="button_message"><a class="button buy_btn" href="https://maevedevs.itch.io/farm-rpg/purchase">Download Now</a><span class="buy_message"><span class="sub">Name your own price</span></span></div></div></div><div class="columns"><div class="left_col column"><div class="formatted_description user_formatted"><p><strong><img src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzE3ODQ3NTI3LmdpZg==/original/AYMYfG.gif" loading="lazy"></strong>
</p>
<p><strong><em>In development: This Assets package is currently under development.</em></strong></p>
<h3><img src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzE3ODU1MDYxLmdpZg==/original/2b7k3H.gif" loading="lazy"></h3>
<h4>🌼 Farm RPG&nbsp;Assets - 16x16, 32x32:&nbsp;</h4>
<p><em><strong>&nbsp;Discover a charming world with our adorable farm assets, specially designed to bring your RPG to life! With a delightful style and bright colors, each item is carefully crafted in a unique palette that evokes warmth and fun.&nbsp;</strong></em>
</p>
<h4></h4>
<h4>✨ Features:</h4>
<ul><li><strong><em>&nbsp;Dimensions: 16x16, 32x32, perfect for any RPG project.&nbsp;</em></strong>
</li><li><strong><em>Format: PNG spritesheets. Compatible with any engine that supports PNG files and spritesheets.<p>Please note that some engines or automated import systems may require manual configuration depending on your workflow. Engine-specific support or custom-formatted versions are not included with this package.<strong></strong></p></em></strong></li><li><strong><em><p>Characters are designed in a 32×32 format using 16 pixels per unit.
</p>
<p>The pack includes two character versions:
</p>
<p>• A modular version with separated PNG parts, allowing full customization with different eyes, hairstyles, skin tones, and more.
</p>
<p>• A premade version for users who prefer ready-to-use characters without building them from scratch. In the premade version, characters only include right-facing sprites. Left-facing movement can be achieved through sprite flipping (flip/mirror) via engine settings or code</p></em></strong></li><li><strong><em>Everything uses 16 pixels per unit!</em></strong><strong></strong></li><li><strong><em>&nbsp;Cute Style: Designs that enchant, with lovely details capturing the essence of rural life.&nbsp;</em></strong>
</li><li><strong><em>&nbsp;Vibrant Colors: An exclusive palette that brings joy and energy to your game, ideal for attracting players of all ages.</em></strong>
</li></ul>
<p><span style="background-color: var(--itchio_white_back); color: inherit; font-size: inherit"></span>
</p>
<figure><img src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzE3ODcyNjU0LmdpZg==/original/e3T64t.gif" loading="lazy"></figure>
<h3><em>Characters in 32×32 format, but with 16 pixels per unit!<br></em></h3>
<h3><em>Simple Animations:</em></h3>
<ul><li><em><strong>Idle - 4 frames&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong></em>
</li><li><em><strong>Walk -&nbsp; 6 frames&nbsp;</strong></em>
</li><li><em><strong>Run -8 frames&nbsp;</strong></em>
</li></ul>
<p><span></span>
</p>
<h3><em>Work Animations:</em></h3>
<ul><li><em><strong>Pickaxe - 6 frames&nbsp;</strong></em>
</li><li><em><strong>Shovel - 5 frames</strong></em>
</li><li><em><strong>Hoe - 6 frames&nbsp;
</strong></em>
</li><li><em><strong>Axe - 6 frames&nbsp;</strong></em>
</li><li><em><strong>Sickle&nbsp;- 6 frames&nbsp;</strong></em>
</li><li><em><strong>Watering - 8 frames&nbsp;</strong></em>
</li><li><em><strong>Picking up items - 4 Frames (Idle holding items and&nbsp;Walking and running with items)&nbsp;</strong></em>
</li></ul>
<p><span></span>
</p>
<h3><em>Combat Animations:</em></h3>
<p><span></span>
</p>
<ul><li><em><strong>Sword -&nbsp; 10 frames</strong></em>
</li><li><em><strong>Damage, - 4 frames</strong></em>
</li><li><em><strong>Dead - 4 frames</strong></em>
</li><li><em><strong>Bow and Arrow - 7 Frames</strong></em>
</li><li><em><strong>Magic/ Healing - 6 Frames</strong></em>
</li></ul>
<p><span></span>
</p>
<h3><em>Fishing Animations:</em></h3>
<ul><li><em><strong>Fishing (&nbsp;</strong></em><em><strong>Casting - 15 frames,&nbsp;</strong></em><em><strong>Wait/idle - 4 frames,&nbsp;</strong></em><em><strong>Hooked - 8 Frames,</strong></em><em><strong>&nbsp;Roll - 4 Frames,&nbsp;</strong></em><em><strong>&nbsp;Captured - 4 Frames&nbsp;</strong></em>)
</li></ul>
<h3><em>Horse Animations:</em></h3>
<ul><li><em><strong><em><em>Horse - (&nbsp;</em><em>Run - 6 Frames,&nbsp;&nbsp;</em><em>Idle - 2 frames )</em></em></strong></em>
</li></ul>
<p><span></span>
</p>
<h3><em>Others Animations:</em></h3>
<ul><li><em><strong>Bicycle - 4 Frames</strong></em>
</li><li><em><strong>Broomstick - 4 Frames</strong></em>
</li><li><em><strong>Climbing - 5 Frames</strong></em>
</li><li><em><strong>Sitting - 1 Frame</strong></em>
</li><li><em><strong>Umbrella (</strong></em><em><strong>Idle - 4 Frames,&nbsp;</strong></em><em><strong>Walk - 6 Frames,&nbsp;</strong></em><em><strong>Running - 8 Frames )</strong></em>
