on_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/hawkgamedev"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzEzMjUxNDY2LnBuZw==/25x25%23/A1GHPH.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/hawkgamedev">hawkgamedev</a></span><span title="2026-06-20 21:04:08" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/16329199">4 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Hello, is it me or you meant to do dirt over grass here but its the same for some reason is repeated... this is an example taken from spring, it would be super useful for me to have dirt over grass as an option.<img src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzI3OTg5NzUzLnBuZw==/original/UsqvHp.png" loading="lazy"></p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:16487997,&quot;id&quot;:16279298}" id="post-16279298" class="community_post has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/coldforge-studios"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzI2MTYxMjY4LnBuZw==/25x25%23/PPaSEg.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/coldforge-studios">NoDev Studios</a></span><span title="2026-06-12 20:29:57" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/16279298">12 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Hey again, loved the update! Just curious if there were any sprites in your pack that would let me create a ramp up to a cliff section similar to the one in this screenshot:&nbsp;<a href="https://imgur.com/a/FwqAjya" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">https://imgur.com/a/FwqAjya<br><br></a>I have also sent you an email, again thank you for this amazing pack, worth it!!!</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:17849870,&quot;id&quot;:16277281}" id="post-16277281" class="community_post has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/martinsupiot"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/martinsupiot">martinsupiot</a></span><span title="2026-06-12 12:50:47" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/16277281">12 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>I&#x27;m missing a sprite between walking and swimming. Can you add it?</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:8199172,&quot;id&quot;:16272790}" id="post-16272790" class="community_post has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/daril-maia"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-red.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/daril-maia">Daril Maia</a></span><span title="2026-06-11 17:06:58" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/16272790">13 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>I really liked the package, but I just needed to walk and run with the tools on the character, that is, in his hands, to make it more natural and normal.<font><font></font></font></p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:4482073,&quot;id&quot;:16259720}" id="post-16259720" class="community_post has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/vkgames82"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-gold.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/vkgames82">Vkgames82</a></span><span title="2026-06-09 09:09:59" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/16259720">15 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="downvotes">(-1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Am I allowed to use this in my hackathon project, considering it&#x27;s a public competition?</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:2921290,&quot;id&quot;:16212534}" id="post-16212534" class="community_post has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/william-34"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/william-34">William 34</a></span><span title="2026-06-01 12:22:27" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/16212534">23 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Very great asset pack!&nbsp;I love the character customization options. Only thing I wish was that there was at least one option for glasses. And of course, a few&nbsp;more options for clothing would be great too. Thanks again for all the incredible assets!</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:14610598,&quot;id&quot;:16198575}" id="post-16198575" class="community_post has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/mhoufc"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-gold.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/mhoufc">mhoufc</a></span><span title="2026-05-30 16:27:17" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/16198575">25 days ago</a></span> <span class="edit_message">(3 edits)</span> <span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>I am struggling to setup the tilemap for the&nbsp;Tileset Grass Cliff Tileset Summer, I know how to setup the tiles for normal terrain but unsure when it comes to the bottom of the cliffs as they are 2 tiles high?<br><a href="https://maevedevs.itch.io/farm-rpg"><br><br></a><a href="https://maevedevs.itch.io/farm-rpg">https://maevedevs.itch.io/farm-rpg<img src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzI3NTc1MDQzLnBuZw==/original/tsEHY2.png" loading="lazy"></a><br></p>
<p><br></p>
<p>Thanks :)</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:17677016,&quot;id&quot;:16190029}" id="post-16190029" class="community_post has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/meonsi"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-cyan.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/meonsi">meonsi</a></span><span title="2026-05-29 12:50:17" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/16190029">26 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>I saw Farm RPG - Tiny Asset Pack on the unity asset store; did you happen to upload it?</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:13447471,&quot;id&quot;:16053309}" id="post-16053309" class="community_post has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/textf"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-cyan.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/textf">textf</a></span><span title="2026-05-09 05:20:54" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/16053309">46 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>I&#x27;m very happy to see your update. Thank you very much for your update.</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:328120,&quot;id&quot;:16049785}" id="post-16049785" class="community_post has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/skywolfgamestudios"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzI1OTAyOTQucG5n/25x25%23/6IplMS.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/skywolfgamestudios">SkywolfGameStudios</a></span><span title="2026-05-08 15:09:02" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/16049785">47 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Thank you kindly for this asset pack. I’ve been reviewing different farming RPG packs over the last two days&nbsp;for a small mobile project I’m working on, and yours stood out as the best fit &mdash; especially since I’m not a 2D artist. If the project does well, I’d be happy to support your work further and I really appreciate what you’re creating here.</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:17309028,&quot;id&quot;:16028908}" id="post-16028908" class="community_post has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/orchidbutterfly"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-gold.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/orchidbutterfly">orchid.butterfly</a></span><span title="2026-05-05 00:43:42" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/16028908">51 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Wow, I love all the stuff included for the characters! This is very beautiful.&nbsp; I do hope that there will eventually be more clothing options, but other than that, totally impressed and very happy with my purchase. Thank you!</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:16487997,&quot;id&quot;:16003034}" id="post-16003034" class="community_post has_vote_column has_replies"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/coldforge-studios"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzI2MTYxMjY4LnBuZw==/25x25%23/PPaSEg.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/coldforge-studios">NoDev Studios</a></span><span title="2026-05-01 08:28:36" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/16003034">54 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Amazing Pack I bought it a few days ago, I just had a few questions regrading the Pick Up animations. In one of your demo screenshots it shows picking up crops and boxes etc. but when I look at the sprite sheet the player isnt carrying anything. So how do I combine said animations?</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:6343539,&quot;id&quot;:16003213}" id="post-16003213" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/maevedevs"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzI0MTQxNzA5LmpwZw==/25x25%23/IjkjbR.jpg)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/maevedevs">Maeve</a></span><span title="2026-05-01 09:15:02" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/16003213">54 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p></p><p>Hi! Thank you for your support 😊
 The items are not part of the pickup animation &mdash; they are separate sprites.
 The carrying effect needs to be handled in your game logic by displaying the item together with the player during the animation.
</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:13683072,&quot;id&quot;:15987036}" id="post-15987036" class="community_post has_vote_column has_replies"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/q3korea"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzIzODQ3NjIwLmpwZw==/25x25%23/YkZP1J.jpg)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/q3korea">Q3Korea</a></span><span title="2026-04-28 23:51:36" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15987036">57 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Hello! I sent you a Discord message a few days ago. Are you no longer active on Discord? Thx! :)</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:6343539,&quot;id&quot;:15987084}" id="post-15987084" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply has_replies"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/maevedevs"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzI0MTQxNzA5LmpwZw==/25x25%23/IjkjbR.jpg)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/maevedevs">Maeve</a></span><span title="2026-04-28 23:58:47" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15987084">57 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Hello! I’m no longer using Discord, but you can contact me via email at <strong>farmrpgassetpack@gmail.com</strong></p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies"><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:13