 class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/maevedevs"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzI0MTQxNzA5LmpwZw==/25x25%23/IjkjbR.jpg)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/maevedevs">Maeve</a></span><span title="2026-04-25 17:40:44" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15960302">60 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>I&#x27;m also not sure if I fully understood your question! If you have any doubts, feel free to send me an email with more detailed information so I can better assist you.</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies"><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:14610598,&quot;id&quot;:15965913}" id="post-15965913" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/mhoufc"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-gold.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/mhoufc">mhoufc</a></span><span title="2026-04-26 17:18:36" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15965913">59 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>It&#x27;s ok, I was just looking for the log sprite you can use after chopping down a tree :)</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:4763817,&quot;id&quot;:15958421}" id="post-15958421" class="community_post has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/yuminoona"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzE0MjcwOTkwLmpwZw==/25x25%23/D%2B5G9%2B.jpg)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/yuminoona">YumiNoona</a></span><span title="2026-04-25 09:15:37" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15958421">60 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>hey i just brought this asset pack loving it<br>just one issue can you share aseprite files of the tilesets its really confusing to build a town</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:1427767,&quot;id&quot;:15900342}" id="post-15900342" class="community_post has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/arsilgames"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-red.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/arsilgames">ArsilGames</a></span><span title="2026-04-15 23:11:26" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15900342">70 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Hi! I just wanted to say your Farm RPG Assets pack looks absolutely beautiful 🌼✨
</p>
<p>The art style is adorable, the colors feel warm and vibrant, and everything has so much charm. You did an amazing job bringing the farm atmosphere to life.
</p>
<p>Really lovely work &mdash; congratulations!
Sorry if my English is not perfect, I’m a Spanish speaker.</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:16771461,&quot;id&quot;:15889765}" id="post-15889765" class="community_post has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/polanking"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-cyan.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/polanking">polanking</a></span><span title="2026-04-14 06:25:49" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15889765">71 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p><font><font></font></font></p><p>Hi!</p>
<p>I’ve just sent you an email with a question about some item icons in your asset pack, along with a screenshot.</p>
<p>Thank you very much for your work!</p><p><font><font></font></font></p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:9053488,&quot;id&quot;:15886105}" id="post-15886105" class="community_post has_vote_column has_replies"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/fatalitiko"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-gold.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/fatalitiko">Fatalitiko</a></span><span title="2026-04-13 15:28:32" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15886105">72 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Some tilesets, like the “Doors, Windows, and Chimneys” one, don&#x27;t work properly in Unity, at least.</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>The doors are too close together, so the Sprite Editor detects them as a single entity. And this happens with many other tilesets as well.
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>And there&#x27;s no way to fix it in Unity&mdash;at least, not that I&#x27;ve found.
</p>
<p>
</p>
<p>Can you help me fix this?
</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:6343539,&quot;id&quot;:15886236}" id="post-15886236" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/maevedevs"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzI0MTQxNzA5LmpwZw==/25x25%23/IjkjbR.jpg)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/maevedevs">Maeve</a></span><span title="2026-04-13 15:53:43" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15886236">72 days ago</a></span> <span class="edit_message">(1 edit)</span> <span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Hello! These tilesets need to be manually adjusted so they appear in the position you want. They are not modular.</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:16875623,&quot;id&quot;:15819370}" id="post-15819370" class="community_post disabled has_vote_column deleted has_replies is_deleted"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><div class="avatar_container"><div style="background-image: url(https://static.itch.io/images/frog-sad.svg)" class="post_avatar"></div></div><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><strong class="name_placeholder">Deleted post</strong></span><span title="2026-04-02 17:15:22" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15819370">83 days ago</a></span></div><div class="post_content"><div class="post_body"><em class="deleted_message">Deleted <span class="2026-04-02 17:47:04">83 days ago</span></em></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:6343539,&quot;id&quot;:15819377}" id="post-15819377" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/maevedevs"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzI0MTQxNzA5LmpwZw==/25x25%23/IjkjbR.jpg)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/maevedevs">Maeve</a></span><span title="2026-04-02 17:16:37" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15819377">83 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Thank you for your feedback! I will improve the organization of the pack in the next update</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:16761904,&quot;id&quot;:15810539}" id="post-15810539" class="community_post has_vote_column has_replies"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/darksoulsfarmer"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-blue.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/darksoulsfarmer">DarksoulsFarmer</a></span><span title="2026-04-01 17:17:40" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15810539">84 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Just wanted to say this pack is really great, the style, variety, and overall quality are amazing. It’s been a joy to work with so far.
</p>
<p>I was also wondering if there’s any rough timeline for the next update? And if possible, do you plan to include more character customization options in the future, like additional hairstyles, clothing, or maybe even hats?
</p>
<p>Thanks again for the awesome work!
</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:6343539,&quot;id&quot;:15819655}" id="post-15819655" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/maevedevs"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzI0MTQxNzA5LmpwZw==/25x25%23/IjkjbR.jpg)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/maevedevs">Maeve</a></span><span title="2026-04-02 17:55:21" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15819655">83 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p></p><p>Hi! Thank you so much for your comment and suggestion! In the future, it will definitely be a great idea to add more customization options for the character.
</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:6225665,&quot;id&quot;:15799050}" id="post-15799050" class="community_post has_vote_column has_replies"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/lrcoliver"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/lrcoliver">LrColiver</a></span><span title="2026-03-31 11:13:41" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15799050">85 days ago</a></span> <span class="edit_message">(1 edit)</span> <span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Oi, tudo bem?&nbsp;<br>Estava tentando contato com você para ver se aceita um pedido relativamente simples que eu pagaria a parte, você tem discord ou outro meio para contato?&nbsp;<br>Tentei o twitter, mas não me deu a opção para mandar mensagens :/</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_ac