v></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:8047407,&quot;id&quot;:15794438}" id="post-15794438" class="community_post has_vote_column has_replies"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/taxalottle-syndicate"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzIxODg1MjY1LnBuZw==/25x25%23/YRX9sW.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/taxalottle-syndicate">Taxalottle Syndicate</a></span><span title="2026-03-30 21:00:33" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15794438">86 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Hello! Great pack, I just have a few things. First off, amazing art. I have two problems though.&nbsp;Your naming and organization are really bad. It takes forever to find anything. I also feel it was designed for specific scenarios. For instance, Having a pier that goes up looks weird because there is no sand splatter asset for up, only down. The cabinets are also really lacking. I tried to make a U-shape, but there are no end stoppers. I ended up having to make my own assets forthese.</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:6343539,&quot;id&quot;:15794856}" id="post-15794856" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/maevedevs"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzI0MTQxNzA5LmpwZw==/25x25%23/IjkjbR.jpg)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/maevedevs">Maeve</a></span><span title="2026-03-30 21:41:02" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15794856">86 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p></p><p>Hello! Thank you for the feedback!
