tn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:14610598,&quot;id&quot;:15639329}" id="post-15639329" class="community_post has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/mhoufc"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-gold.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/mhoufc">mhoufc</a></span><span title="2026-03-04 23:42:59" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15639329">112 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Just wondering if there are any plans for adding shops/stores to buy stuff from?</p><p>Thanks!</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:8308457,&quot;id&quot;:15636519}" id="post-15636519" class="community_post has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/chrisgv"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-red.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/chrisgv">chrisgv</a></span><span title="2026-03-04 16:53:31" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15636519">112 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Is there animal products? Like milk for cow, wool for sheep etc.? I can&#x27;t seem to find it.</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:16365362,&quot;id&quot;:15636202}" id="post-15636202" class="community_post has_vote_column has_replies"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/dawekluhf"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-red.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/dawekluhf">dawekluhf</a></span><span title="2026-03-04 16:02:23" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15636202">112 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Hi, i cant find doors texture in doors, windows and curtains.png i can find only curtains</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:6343539,&quot;id&quot;:15636427}" id="post-15636427" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/maevedevs"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzI0MTQxNzA5LmpwZw==/25x25%23/IjkjbR.jpg)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/maevedevs">Maeve</a></span><span title="2026-03-04 16:37:12" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15636427">112 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>It is located in the <strong>Exterior\Houses</strong> folder.</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:1728140,&quot;id&quot;:15545161}" id="post-15545161" class="community_post has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/darcioan