ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>hey, ive got a question, is there a color palette you use? if so, could you add it into the pack?<br></p><p>there are some items id like to add to my game (think food, background UI) that might need the palette.</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:3202350,&quot;id&quot;:15509288}" id="post-15509288" class="community_post has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/cabanasds"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/cabanasds">cabanas.ds</a></span><span title="2026-02-19 11:32:11" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15509288">125 days ago</a></span> <span class="edit_message">(1 edit)</span> <span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>cool pack, badly organized.&nbsp; took me a while to find the tilesets!!</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:9452844,&quot;id&quot;:15507490}" id="post-15507490" class="community_post has_vote_column has_replies"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/2084840326"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-blue.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/2084840326">2084840326</a></span><span title="2026-02-19 02:18:41" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15507490">125 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Where is the seed that the player is holding up?<img src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzI1NjY4NDI1LnBuZw==/original/O2Vk58.png" loading="lazy">？<img src="https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzI1NjY4NDM5LnBuZw==/original/8ZTuIr.png" loading="lazy">？I only found the &#x27;Crops&#x27; file.</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:6343539,&quot;id&quot;:15507586}" id="post-15507586" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/maevedevs"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzI0MTQxNzA5LmpwZw==/25x25%23/IjkjbR.jpg)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/maevedevs">Maeve</a></span><span title="2026-02-19 02:40:05" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15507586">125 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Hi! Thank you so much for letting me know about this issue! I’ve just fixed it and added the correct seed pack icons. You can find them in the “Icons” folder. 😊</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:16198792,&quot;id&quot;:15465480}" id="post-15465480" class="community_post has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/ricardokersch"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-red.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/ricardokersch">RicardoKersch</a></span><span title="2026-02-12 19:01:27" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15465480">132 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Hi, I&#x27;m starting the development of an indie game using your Asset Pack. I found your work wonderful, congratulations. Some details can already be seen here: <a href="https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLVkJlPLXoH7mkXmFh9adKDg7fcoFYbeQL&si=pRZezWbcbLh10Wh3" referrerpolicy="origin" rel="nofollow noopener">https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLVkJlPLXoH7mkXmFh9adKDg7fcoFYbeQL&si=pRZezWbc...</a></p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:16307438,&quot;id&quot;:15420414}" id="post-15420414" class="community_post has_vote_column"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/niarthgin"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-gold.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/niarthgin">niarthgin</a></span><span title="2026-02-07 08:27:57" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15420414">137 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Hey there! I just picked up your pixel pack, and I felt compelled to reach out and let you know how impressed I am. First off, the art style is absolutely stunning&mdash;the colors are so vibrant and really pop off the screen. ❤️</p>
<p>I was honestly surprised by the sheer volume of assets included, especially the seasonal variations. It’s rare to find a pack that feels this comprehensive while it&#x27;s still technically under development. You’ve clearly put a lot of heart into the details, and it shows!</p>
<p>I’m curious about the future of this project: do you have any plans to include monsters or enemy sprites at some point? I’d love to see your take on some creatures in this style!</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:16254773,&quot;id&quot;:15409785}" id="post-15409785" class="community_post has_vote_column has_replies"><div id="last-post" class="post_anchor"></div><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/kenzho"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-gold.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/kenzho">Kenzho</a></span><span title="2026-02-05 00:44:47" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15409785">140 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Just bought the all in packs, btw how to create the waterfall animation ? I can&#x27;t find the sprite sheet for the waterfall ?</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies top_level_replies"><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:6343539,&quot;id&quot;:15409970}" id="post-15409970" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply has_replies"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/maevedevs"><div style="background-image: url(https://img.itch.zone/aW1nLzI0MTQxNzA5LmpwZw==/25x25%23/IjkjbR.jpg)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/maevedevs">Maeve</a></span><span title="2026-02-05 01:41:14" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15409970">140 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"><span class="upvotes">(+1)</span></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>The waterfall can be found in Farm\Tileset\Modular.</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div><div class="community_post_replies"><div data-post="{&quot;user_id&quot;:16254773,&quot;id&quot;:15410826}" id="post-15410826" class="community_post has_vote_column is_reply"><div class="post_grid"><div class="post_votes"><a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote up" class="vote_up_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_up"><polygon points="2 18 12 6 22 18" /></svg></a> <a data-register_action="community_vote" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" title="Vote down" class="vote_down_btn vote_btn"><svg width="20" height="20" version="1.1" role="img" aria-hidden viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="svgicon icon_vote_down"><polygon points="2 6 12 18 22 6" /></svg></a></div><a class="avatar_container" href="https://itch.io/profile/kenzho"><div style="background-image: url(/static/images/frog-gold.png)" class="post_avatar"></div></a><div class="post_header"><span class="post_author"><a href="https://itch.io/profile/kenzho">Kenzho</a></span><span title="2026-02-05 05:44:40" class="post_date"><a href="https://itch.io/post/15410826">139 days ago</a></span><span class="vote_counts"></span></div><div class="post_content"><div dir="auto" class="post_body user_formatted"><p>Found it !! I love your assets, thanks for the hardwork ! This is help 60% of my game assets</p></div><div class="post_footer"><a data-register_action="community_reply" href="https://itch.io/login?return_to=https%3A%2F%2Fmaevedevs.itch.io%2Ffarm-rpg&amp;intent=community" class="post_action reply_btn">Reply</a></div></div></div></div></div></div><script id="vote_counts_tpl" type="text/template"><% if (up_score > 0) { %><span class="upvotes">(+{{up_score}}